        "descriptions": [
          {
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "The Arm Mali GPU kernel driver allows privilege escalation or information disclosure because GPU memory operations are mishandled, leading to a use-after-free. This affects Bifrost r0p0 through r28p0 before r29p0, Valhall r19p0 through r28p0 before r29p0, and Midgard r4p0 through r30p0."
          },
          {
            "lang": "es",
            "value": "El controlador del kernel de Arm Mali GPU, permite una escalada de privilegios o una divulgaci\u00f3n de informaci\u00f3n porque las operaciones de la memoria de la GPU son manejadas inapropiadamente, conllevando a un uso de la memoria previamente liberada.&#xa0;Esto afecta a Bifrost versiones r0p0 hasta r28p0, anteriores a r29p0, Valhall versiones r19p0 hasta r28p0 anteriores a r29p0 y Midgard versiones r4p0 hasta r30p0"
          }
        ],
